itemDescription.value: Worked at Lloyds Bank at 16 for 4 years before turning professional as a session keyboard player
British film, television and theatre director
Architect Brady Mallalieu Architects and president of RIBA 2011 - 2013
former wife of Hon. Gerald Lascelles (1919-2007)
English poet and short story writer
British water polo player and coach
Professor of Oncology at St George's, University of London and member of the United Kingdom Independence Party (UKIP)
